oai_dc:dc.dc:title: STRUCTURAL RESPONSE OF DOLOS IN WAVES
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Tedesco, Joseph W.
McGill, Preston B.
Melby, Jeffrey A.
McDougal, William G.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: dolos
dolos in waves
structural response to waves
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Several numerical models for estimating wave forces on dolosse are presented. These models are incorporated into a finite element method (FEM) analysis of a 42-ton unit. The results of the analysis permit identification of unit structural failure with respect to wave conditions.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 21 (1988): Proceedings of 21st Conference on Coastal Engineering, Torremolinos, Spain, 1988.; 181
